Description: XFB Radio Automation Software
 XFB Radio Automation Software is a comprehensive solution designed for
 professional radio stations and broadcasting environments. The software
 provides full accessibility support for visually impaired users through
 ORCA screen reader integration, complete keyboard navigation, audio feedback,
 and braille display support.
 .
 Key accessibility features:
  * Full ORCA screen reader compatibility with live region updates
  * Complete keyboard navigation - no mouse required
  * Audio feedback for all user actions and system events
  * Braille display support via BrlTTY integration
  * Customizable accessibility preferences and verbosity levels
  * WCAG 2.1 AA compliance for web-based components
  * Context-sensitive help system with audio descriptions
 .
 Broadcasting features:
  * Professional audio playback and recording capabilities
  * Playlist management with drag-and-drop support
  * Live streaming integration with Icecast/Shoutcast
  * Automated scheduling and crossfading
  * Real-time audio processing and effects
  * Multi-format audio support (MP3, FLAC, WAV, OGG)
  * Database-driven music library management
 .
 This version is optimized for Ubuntu 20.04 LTS and newer systems with
 comprehensive ORCA screen reader support.